# 🧑‍💻 SmartBridge Full-Stack Freelancer Platform

This repository contains a full-stack web application built as part of the **SmartBridge Internship Program**. The platform enables **clients to post projects**, **freelancers to browse and bid**, and includes **real-time chat**, **role-based dashboards**, and **admin tools** for managing the freelancing workflow.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 **User Authentication** – Secure login/register with JWT  
- 🧑‍💼 **Client Dashboard** – Post, update, and manage projects  
- 🧑‍🔧 **Freelancer Dashboard** – Browse projects, submit proposals  
- 💬 **Real-Time Chat** – Clients & freelancers can communicate within projects  
- 📁 **Work Submission** – Freelancers can submit completed work  
- ✅ **Approval Flow** – Clients review and approve work  
- 🛡️ **Admin Controls** – Admin dashboard to monitor platform activity and resolve disputes  
- 🔔 **Notifications** – Instant updates for project status and messages  
- 💻 **Fully Responsive** – Mobile and desktop-friendly UI  

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Layer        | Technology           |
|--------------|----------------------|
| Frontend     | React.js, Bootstrap, Axios, Material UI, Framer Motion |
| Backend      | Node.js, Express.js  |
| Database     | MongoDB (via Mongoose) |
| Auth         | JWT (JSON Web Tokens) |
| Realtime     | Socket.IO (for chat & updates) |
| Deployment   | Vercel (Frontend), Render (Backend) |

---
